lead_paragraph: Chris Parmelee homered twice in his first start for the Yankees, Carlos Beltran added two more big hits to his huge series and New York's bats broke loose late in a 12-6 victory over the Los Angeles Angels on Wednesday night.

headline.print_headline: Parmelee, Beltran Power Yankees to 12-6 Win Over Angels
